   Although there may be an unlimited number of questions about the Idaho
   National Engineering and Environmental Laboratory, answers to most
   inquiries can be obtained by calling a relative handful of individuals
   or organizations at the INEEL or the U.S. Department of Energy. The
   INEELs Web site contains links and contacts for most questions asked
   about the INEEL. Additionally, and for your convenience, here are some
   of INEELs most frequently called numbers:

   INEEL Operator Assistance
   (208) 526-0111

   Employment
   (208) 526-1700 - Opportunities
   (208) 526-0182 - Verification

   Media Inquiries
   (208) 526-5652 - Rick Dale
   (208) 526-8646 - John Walsh

   Benefits/Insurance
   (208) 526-1001
   (208) 526-2000 - an options menu

   Diversity Initiatives/Equal Employment Opportunity
   (208) 526-0085
   (208) 526-9169

   Affirmative Action
   (208) 526-9169

   Educational Outreach
   (208) 526-0318 - Precollege Programs
   (208) 526-3401 - University Programs
   (208) 526-0022 - Professional Development

   DOE Office of Inspector General
   (800) 541-1625

